nmap <leader>j <Action>(GotoFile)
nmap <leader>k <Action>(GotoAction)
nmap <leader>tt :NERDTreeToggle<CR>
nmap <leader>tf :NERDTreeFind<CR>
nmap <leader>a <Action>(Annotate)
nmap <leader>r <Action>(Refactorings.QuickListPopupAction)
nmap <leader>d <Action>(EditorDuplicate)
nmap <leader>w <Action>(SaveAll)
nmap <leader>f <Action>(FindInPath)
nmap <leader>x <Action>(CloseContent)
nmap <leader>X <Action>(CloseAllEditorsButActive)
nmap <leader>h <Action>(HighlightUsagesInFile)
nmap <leader>n <Action>(Go.NewGoFile)
nmap <leader>gi <Action>(GotoImplementation)
nmap <leader>gd <Action>(GotoDeclarationOnly)
nmap <leader>gs <Action>(GotoSuperMethod)
nmap <leader>ge <Action>(GotoNextError)
nmap <leader>gu <Action>(FindUsages)
nmap <leader>vp <Action>(ParameterInfo)
nmap <leader>vr <Action>(RecentFiles)
nmap <leader>vd <Action>(QuickJavaDoc)
nmap <leader>vt <Action>(QuickTypeDefinition)
nmap <leader>ve <Action>(ShowErrorDescription)
nmap <leader>i i<SPACE><ESC>r
nmap <leader>cc <Plug>(CommentMotion)
nmap <leader>c<SPACE> <Plug>(CommentLine)
vmap <leader>cc <Plug>(CommentMotionV)
vmap <leader>c<SPACE> <Plug>(CommentMotionV)
nmap <C-O> <Action>(Forward)
nmap <C-I> <Action>(Back)
nmap <C-J> <Action>(PreviousTab)
nmap <C-K> <Action>(NextTab)
nmap <C-down> <Action>(MoveLineDown)
nmap <C-up> <Action>(MoveLineUp)
nmap <C-N> <Action>(SelectNextOccurrence)
nmap <C-S-N> <Action>(SelectAllOccurrences)
nmap <A-P> <Action>(UnselectPreviousOccurrence)
nmap <A-X> <Action>(FindNext)
nmap <leader>o mao<ESC>`a
nmap <leader>O maO<ESC>`a
nmap <Home> ^
nmap <End> $
nmap <A-j> <Action>(PrevSplitter)
nmap <A-k> <Action>(NextSplitter)

map <leader>y <Action>($Copy)